This page documents the data structures used in '''[[Secret of Mana]]''' (US version).

==Enemy Stats==

===Enemy Stats Table===
Located at ROM offset '''$102655''' (verified via pattern analysis). Each entry is '''29 bytes'''.

'''Note:''' The previously documented offset $101dfa appears to contain different data.

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00 || 1 || HP (single byte, e.g., Rabite = 20)
|-
| $01 || 1 || Unknown (often duplicates HP)
|-
| $02-$07 || 6 || Flags and type data
|-
| $08 || 1 || Combat attribute 1
|-
| $09 || 1 || Combat attribute 2
|-
| $0a || 1 || Attack modifier
|-
| $0b || 1 || Defense modifier
|-
| $0c-$0d || 2 || Additional combat values
|-
| $0e-$11 || 4 || Reserved (typically 0xfc 0x7f 0x00 0x00)
|-
| $12-$13 || 2 || Unknown
|-
| $14-$15 || 2 || Experience (encoded format)
|-
| $16-$1c || 7 || Gold and additional data
|}

